OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FIt was one of the most dramatic boom
OL,7,Fand bust spells in football.
OL,9,FGretna FC was a tiny club on the
OL,10,Fborder which only joined the Scottish
OL,11,Fleague system in 2002 after years in
OL,12,FEnglish non-league football.
OL,14,FBankrolled by millionaire Brooks
OL,15,FMileson, they rocketed up the
OL,16,Fdivisions, winning three successive
OL,17,Fpromotions from 2005 to 2007.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
