CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FWith its success, the village which
OL,7,Fwas always known for where runaway
OL,8,Flovers got married, became famous for
OL,9,Fits football team.
OL,11,FAnd in 2006 the romance of the cup
OL,12,Ftook on a whole new meaning as they
OL,13,Fbecame the first third-tier team to
OL,14,Freach the Scottish Cup final.
OL,16,FManager at the time, Rowan Alexander,
OL,17,Fsaid: "I've always had big ambitions,
OL,18,Fand I wanted to go to the Premier
OL,19,FLeague.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,F"I think we broke all sorts of records
OL,7,Fregarding goalscoring charts with
OL,8,FKenny Deuchar. A little village like
OL,9,FGretna and we were pulling in like
OL,10,F3000 fans.
OL,12,FIt was a David vs. Goliath scenario,
OL,13,Fas Gretna FC faced Hearts, who had
OL,14,Fpreviously reached the final 13 times,
OL,15,Fwinning six.
OL,17,F"In the lead up to the tunnel, you can
OL,18,Fyou can just feel the vibe," Rowan,
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,F"The hairs on the back of your neck
OL,7,Fjust stand on end.
OL,9,F"It was just great because the fans,
OL,10,Fthey're all in the little corner on
OL,11,Fthe right hand side. When we came out
OL,12,Fit was just a sea of black and white
OL,13,Fand it took your breath away."
OL,15,F15,000 people turned out in support of
OL,16,FGretna FC, hoping to see the side make
OL,17,Fhistory.
OL,19,FBut their fairytale shattered, after
OL,20,Fthe game finished 1-1 with Hearts
OL,21,Fwinning 4-2 on penalties.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FMidfielder Gavin Skelton, who was a
OL,7,Fkey figure in the side's rise through
OL,8,Fthe leagues and their Scottish cup
OL,9,Frun, said: "What a fantastic
OL,10,Fopportunity, but what a what missed
OL,11,Fopportunity, not just because of the
OL,12,Fpenalties but in the game as the game
OL,13,Fwent on.
OL,15,F"I can remember it being the longest,
OL,16,Floneliest walk up. And I can remember
OL,17,Fstanding in and Craig Gordon standing
OL,18,Fin the goal and I remember thinking,
OL,19,F'I have no idea where I'm going to put
OL,20,Fthis'.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,F"And unfortunately I'm sure he got a
OL,7,Ffinger tip to it and it just went over.
OL,9,F"I can't really remember much after
OL,10,Fthat walking around the pitch or
OL,11,Fgetting my medal. Still disappointed
OL,12,Fand still think 'what if?' but as a
OL,13,Fwhole I remember it as a fantastic
OL,14,Fday."
OL,16,FDespite the crushing defeat in the
OL,17,Ffinal, Gretna's remarkable cup run
OL,18,Fopened an unexpected door: a place in
OL,19,FEurope.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FBut those continental dreams proved
OL,7,Fshort-lived, as Derry City swept them
OL,8,Faside 5`1 in the opening leg.
OL,10,FFans believed they would live to fight
OL,11,Fanother day, but little did they know
OL,12,Fthe club's days were numbered.
OL,14,FAs Mileson's health deteriorated, so
OL,15,Fdid the club's funding and everything
OL,16,Fit had built in such a short space of
OL,17,Ftime, came crashing down just as
OL,18,Fquickly.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FBut out of the ashes formed Gretna FC
OL,7,F2008 - and the focus shifted from
OL,8,Frapid success to long term survival.
OL,10,FIain Martin, Club Secretary, Gretna FC
OL,11,F2008, said: "It was really upsetting
OL,12,Fbecause the whole village got behind
OL,13,Fthe Gretna team, and I know there were
OL,14,Fa few people upset with what happened
OL,15,Fand money going to various folk.
OL,17,F"But there was this desire to make
OL,18,Fsure there was always football.
OL,19,FThere's always been football here
OL,20,Fsince 1946. Football had to continue."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
