FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,FNearly 20 years after the collapse of
OL,7,Fthe original club Gretna FC 2008 is
OL,8,Fstill rebuilding on and off the pitch.
OL,10,FNikki White, Director of Football,
OL,11,FGretna FC 2008, said: "It should
OL,12,Freally be the hub of the community.
OL,13,FAnd that's something that over the
OL,14,Fnext year or so, we really need to be
OL,15,Fkind of putting more of a focus on.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778785872
OL,3,CThe rise, fall and rebirth of football
OL,4,Cin Gretna
OL,6,F"We've got 200 plus kids in the
OL,7,Facademy so I think we need to build
OL,8,Faround them, their parents, and
OL,9,Fgetting fresh fans in. And that's how
OL,10,Fwe're hoping to kind of push forward,
OL,11,Fparticularly next season.
OL,13,F"It'll be all new there and there'll
OL,14,Fbe some big clubs coming down with
OL,15,Fsome big fan bases, which obviously
OL,16,Fhelps with revenue streams"
OL,18,FThe rise of Gretna FC was one of
OL,19,FScottish football's greatest
OL,20,Ffairytales, and its collapse was one
OL,21,Fof its starkest warnings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
